  <figcaption>
    Biochar is a high-grade soil amendment that all research has shown has enormous benefits to the soil. Crop yields have been proven to bump 3-5 times with its use, water retention has in the soil increases, and biochar has also been shown to mitigate many soil borne diseases.
  </figcaption>
  <figcaption>
